\begin{examplebox}{Example 1: Understanding the Gradient Slope of a Line}
Find the slope of a line passing through points $(2, 3)$ and $(6, 11)$.

\textbf{Given:}
\begin{itemize}[nosep]
\item Point 1: $(2, 3)$
\item Point 2: $(6, 11)$
\end{itemize}

\textbf{Required:} Slope of the line

