\section*{Learning Outcomes}
\nopagebreak[4]
\begin{samepage}
\begin{itemize}
    \item \textbf{LO1:} Perform addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division operations on whole numbers with accuracy, demonstrating mastery of computational procedures.
    \item \textbf{LO2:} Apply the rules for operations with integers, including signed number arithmetic, to solve problems involving positive and negative quantities.
    \item \textbf{LO3:} Correctly apply the order of operations (PEMDAS/BODMAS) to evaluate expressions containing multiple operations with whole numbers and integers.
    \item \textbf{LO4:} Translate real-world scenarios into mathematical expressions involving whole numbers and integers, then solve to obtain meaningful answers with appropriate interpretation.
\end{itemize}
