Product of Powers & $a^m \cdot a^n = a^{m+n}$ & $2^3 \cdot 2^4 = 2^7$ \\
Power of a Power & $(a^m)^n = a^{m \cdot n}$ & $(2^3)^2 = 2^6$ \\
Power of a Product & $(ab)^n = a^n \cdot b^n$ & $(2 \cdot 3)^2 = 4 \cdot 9$ \\
