\textbf{10.} A structural beam is modeled by a line passing through $(0, 3)$ and $(6, 9)$. If the beam is rotated $90°$ counterclockwise about the origin, find the equation of the rotated beam. (Hint: Use the rotation matrix with $\theta = 90°$.)
